Package com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models

Class Project

java.lang.Object
com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models.Project
@Entity public class Project extends Object
The database entity for a project. A project is something Students work on within an edition. A project has coaches to help the students and is typically done for or with help of an Organisation.
